        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/g/4bbf92/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2019-05-18T01:09:56.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Well there\u2019s a  mouthful of a tagline!  Not sure how I ended up with this bottle first time trying this producer.   This is some really good QPR juice.  Elegant and pure cherry nose with some earth. Lightish weight and bricking at edge belies its excellent core of fruit.    Juicy acidity gives the wine a wonderful lift.    Good finish and all in all a really good wine for this appellation.   Certainly will go several years further but if you have any is drinking good now</p>",
