        "created_at": "2019-06-01T05:35:32.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>This is one of those treasured estates of the Cote de Chalonnaise that EVERYONE should be aware of.  A long time Neal Rosenthal selection (which is why you rarely see them for sale), every single wine they produce is worth seeking out.  I love their Mercurey Blanc as well -</p>\n<p>Thanks for the note -</p>",
